social_posts.post_text: I was able to raise $2000 for the #IndianResidentialSchoolSurvivorsSociety with the help of @logitech & @streamlabs. Thank you for acknowledging #nativeamericanheritagemonth & fundraising for native causes. Thank you streamlabs for the $1000 donation & thank you to my amazing & generous community for your donations! This chairty hits very close to home as my Grandmother, Mother, Aunts & Uncles are all residential school survivors. Snachailya. 🧡🥰

Happy to be home on my Rez. 🥰
